    rmarkdown,
    testit,
    testthat (>= 2.1.0)
VignetteBuilder: knitr
URL: https://github.com/richelbilderbeek/mauricerinstall/
BugReports: https://github.com/richelbilderbeek/mauricerinstall/issues
SystemRequirements: BEAST2 (https://www.beast2.org/)
